  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0874637cabf445b44aa6cb3553862f49, type: 3}
  m_Name: Mata_1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::PenyakitData
  tagBahagian: Mata
  namaPenyakit: Keratitis
  namaPenyakitEN: Keratitis
  tahapRisiko: Tahap 3
  tahapRisikoEN: Level 3
  gambar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 76a36f0fce40a1a4da8e96a751f8915d, type: 3}
  isGraphic: 0
  punca: Habuk, angin, bakteria, kulat, virus, atau pertumbuhan bulu mata yang tidak
    normal.
  simptom: Kornea menjadi keruh, masalah penglihatan, bengkak, parut, keluar lendir,
    kucing mengecilkan mata (squinting), dan kemerahan.
  tindakan: Rujuk doktor haiwan dan elakkan mata daripada terengsa (irritated).
  maklumatTambahan: Boleh merebak menjadi ulser kornea dan hilang penglihatan. Sukar
    sembuh, selalu menyerang kucing tua, dan rawatan pembedahan buat masa ini tidak
    ada di Malaysia.
  puncaEN: Dust, wind, bacteria, fungi, virus, or abnormal eyelash growth.
  simptomEN: The cornea becomes cloudy, vision problems, swelling, scarring, mucus
    discharge, the cat squints, and redness.
  tindakanEN: Refer to a veterinarian and prevent the eyes from being irritated.
  maklumatTambahanEN: Can spread to become corneal ulcers and loss of vision. Difficult
    to heal, often attacks older cats, and surgical treatment is currently unavailable
    in Malaysia.
